title: Can't make my picks at pick em event
body:
so I tried to make my picks at the pick' em event, but as soon as I press the "Make your picks" the page loops around the sign-in page and the pick'em event page, 

Please help!

replies.body:
I recommend trying from another browser or after clearing your browser data with [this guide.](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies)

Let me know if either of those steps helped.
